## Xcode
# The PencilNotes example is opened through the repo-root PencilNotes.xcworkspace.
# Both the workspace (its contents.xcworkspacedata defines the members) and the
# committed Examples/PencilNotes/PencilNotes.xcodeproj are tracked so a fresh clone
# just opens and resolves — see scripts/generate-pencilnotes.sh for regeneration.
# Other generated projects (e.g. the E2E host) stay ignored.
/E2E/MarkdownE2E/MarkdownE2E.xcodeproj/
*.generated.plist

# User-specific / cache state (incl. the auto-generated workspace inside .xcodeproj).
project.xcworkspace/
*.xcworkspace/xcuserdata/
*.xcworkspace/xcshareddata/
xcuserdata/
**/xcuserdata/
DerivedData/
*.xcuserstate
*.xcscmblueprint
*.xccheckout
build/

